nels floor consoles door panels overhead consoles cockpit systems decorative trims and other products the company operates in the americas europe africa asia and china it has collaboration with fca us llc to produce seating for the chry adient plc designs manufactures and markets a range of seating systems and components for passenger cars commercial vehicles and light trucks including vans pickup trucks and sportcrossover utility vehicles the company operates through seating and interiors segments the seating segment produces automotive seat metal structures and mechanisms foams trims and fabric and complete seat systems the interiors segment produces instrument panels floor consoles door panels overhead consoles cockpit systems decorative trims and other products the company operates in the americas europe africa asia and china it has collaboration with fca us llc to produce seating for the chrysler portal concept vehicles adient plc was incorporated in  and is based in dublin ireland detailed description  north wall quayifscdublin dublin  d hirelandfounded in  employees phone     wwwadientcom key executives for adient plc mr r bruce mcdonald chairman and chief executive officer age  total annual compensation m mr jeffrey m stafeil chief financial officer and executive vice president age  total annual compensation k mr neil e marchuk chief human resources officer and executive vice president age  total annual compensation m mr byron s foster executive vice president age  total annual compensation k mr eric s mitchell executive vice president age  total annual compensation k compensation as of fiscal year  adient plc key developments adient plc declares quarterly cash dividend payable on august   jul   the board of directors of adient plc announced that its board of directors declared a quarterly cash dividend of usd  per ordinary share payable on august   to shareholders of record at the close of business on july   adient plc presents at china business review in s